 ('5','1','Acme A-100',null,'49.99','<p><img width=\"215\" height=\"169\" src=\"/images/acme_a100.jpg\" alt=\"Acme A-100\" />\n1\" x 4\" x 9\"<br />\n100 / Bale<br />\n<em>*In Stock &amp; Ready to Ship<br />\nSame-Day / Next-Day Delivery Within 50 Mi. of Tulsa, OK</em>\n</p>\n<ul>\n	<li>Pure melt-blown polypropylene fibers: the most cost-effective absorption technology today</li>\n	<li>Fast-wicking fibers absorb up to 25 times their weight in hydrocarbon</li>\n	<li>These durable, single-weight pads absorb petroleum based liquids, but never water</li>\n	<li>Ideal when you have to clean up oily spills or drips</li>\n	<li>Great for when you don&#8217;t need the extra absorbency or expense of a universal absorbent</li>\n	<li>Product is sold by net weight &mdash; Pad counts are approximate</li>\n</ul>\n<table cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" class=\"std\">\n	<tr>\n<td class=\"icon hasBorder\">\n<a title=\"Download the chemical compatibility guide in PDF format\" href=\"/downloads/ACME_ChemCompatibility.pdf\">\n<img width=\"56\" height=\"52\" src=\"/images/chem_compat_icon.jpg?1185942751\" alt=\"Chemical compatibility guide for Acme A-100\"/>\n</a>\n</td>\n<td>\n<a title=\"Download the chemical compatibility guide in PDF format\" href=\"/downloads/ACME_ChemCompatibility.pdf\">Chemical compatibility guide for Sorbents</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>','a100_fpo.jpg','215','184','a100_thumb.jpg','59','54','This text is for placement only','1\" x 4\" x 9\"','100 / Bale','1'),
